[31m-## 9. Troubleshooting (common, repo-specific)[m
[31m-[m
[31m-| Symptom | Likely cause | What to check |[m
[31m-|---------|----------------|---------------|[m
[31m-| App exits immediately / “listening” wrong port | Not binding to `PORT` | `src/config/index.js` and `src/server.js` |[m
[31m-| 404 on `/` | Wrong service root or static path | `src/app.js`, `public/index.html` exists |[m
[31m-| Health works, predict fails | Wrong field name or non-video | Field must be **`video`**; MIME must start with `video/` |[m
[31m-| 413 / “File is too large” | Multer limit | `config.maxFileSize` (50 MB) |[m
